OL,5,G0100 Find It, Fix It, Flog It
OL,6,     FIn Wiltshire Henry and Simon meet
OL,7,     FLaura who lives in a collection of
OL,8,     Ffarm buildings. Henry takes a hay
OL,9,     Fcart and Simon falls in love with
OL,10,     Fsome glass collecting jars.
OL,11,G0200 Great British Railway Journeys
OL,12,     FPontyclun to Ebbw Vale Town:
OL,13,     FMichael Portillo travels from
OL,14,     FPontyclun to Ebbw Vale in Wales,
OL,15,     Fvisiting the Royal Mint in
OL,16,     FLlantrisant and Cardiff Arms Park.
OL,17,G0225 Great British Railway Journeys
OL,18,     FNewport to Clevedon: Michael
OL,19,     FPortillo arrives in Newport, where
OL,20,     Fhe learns about the heroism of a
OL,21,     Fyoung boy who was awarded the
OL,22,     FAlbert Medal.
